{"tid":1710039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大出聲明：潛落海底嘅郭位終於出嚟喇","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T06:29:25.000Z","uid":34045,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"876212441dc4f0063a1e8296238bbde55bd5943a","tid":1710039,"uid":34045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"Dear Colleagues and Students, <br />\n <br />\nCheng Yick-chi Building and the Office of the President were forcibly broken into and maliciously damaged last night by a group of unidentified masked people. The violent acts of criminal damage were broadcast by a reporter of one of our student groups. The University strongly condemns all acts of vandalism and criminal damage and reserves the right to pursue legal and other necessary actions against those responsible. <br />\n <br />\nAn investigation committee will be set up to investigate the incident and identify those responsible. Disciplinary actions will be instituted against any CityU students found to be involved.<br />\n <br />\nProfessor Way KUO, President<br />\nProfessor Alex JEN, Provost<br />\nProfessor Jian LU, Vice-President (Research and Technology) and Dean (Graduate Studies)<br />\nProfessor Horace IP, Vice-President (Student Affairs)<br />\nProfessor Matthew LEE, Vice-President (Development and External Relations)<br />\nMr Sunny LEE, Vice-President (Administration)<br />\nProfessor Paul LAM, Chief-of-Staff<br />\nProfessor Eric CHUI, Dean of Students<br />\nProfessor Richard YUEN, Acting Director of Communications and Public Relations<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n各位同事，同學：<br />\n <br />\n鄭翼之樓及校長辦公室於昨天晚上遭到惡意刑事破壞，多處地方受損毁，其間更有城大學生組織記者把非法暴力破壞行為即時上網。大學強烈譴責所有刑事破壞行為，並對相關人等保留一切法律及其他責任的追究權利。 <br />\n <br />\n大學將成立調查委會，調查事件及確定渉案人士，如查出有城大學生涉案，將會以既定紀律處分程序，嚴肅處理。<br />\n <br />\n校長郭位教授<br />\n學務副校長任廣禹教授<br />\n副校長（研究及科技）及研究生院院長呂堅教授<br />\n副校長（學生事務）葉豪盛教授<br />\n副校長（發展及對外關係）李國安教授<br />\n副校長（行政）李惠光先生<br />\n秘書長林群聲教授<br />\n學務長崔永康教授<br />\n署理傳訊及公關處處長袁國傑教授<br />\n<br />\ncbc影到碌假鳩就即刻浮返上嚟,嬲嬲豬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhOLJ0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhOLJ0V.jpg&h=6e112a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e775dc5aac517b08bb8a256838bc5f8c1aafc6c","tid":1710039,"uid":270214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"假9係咪佛仔嚟？呢個像好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8quSo2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8quSo2T.png&h=7b3c4411&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba5fb60cea8b7d6545e58879019d6371675ff26","tid":1710039,"uid":34045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e775dc5aac517b08bb8a256838bc5f8c1aafc6c","tid":1710039,"uid":270214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"假9係咪佛仔嚟？呢個像好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8quSo2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8quSo2T.png&h=7b3c4411&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"郭位個人像嚟，可能佢無聊嗰陣拎落嚟J自己"},{"pid":"2c343007c665476cb080285312c1ebc220ae99c5","tid":1710039,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"假鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0abfa8cd75b312efccae412681c8641d62e3e4","tid":1710039,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:30:01.000Z","msg":"邊度假鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981f03691bfba88a7e083c078e8434370ec2b0a2","tid":1710039,"uid":277235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"到而家淨係掛住自己個OFFICE <br />\n食屎啦郭位"},{"pid":"790d8077595b7470b7b2b93bbe7c4ac28ef9134f",